MsgEn:
If you can obtain the strength to guard Cecily 
from the Black Knight's malevolent hands, 
I will say no more about Leo.

Do not worry about us; 
We will offer assistance 
to the people of Phindym.

Of course, it is not fear that drives us;
battling Dragons is beyond imagination.
For us, the closest emotion is that of taboo.

We can go out somewhere to 
fight or search for things; 
that’s something we can do.
